name: Dissemination
description:
*** Log Book – Phosphor Labs ***
     entry +22.02.08 # 0730PM 

- As I was pushing the laboratory's phosphors to reproduce stronger and stronger electron beams, an unexpected event occurred – I lost all control of my station. 
It is as if an electrostatic entity has taken over every piece of equipment as well as my sanity, I'm starting to feel scrutinized and wrapped in this electric haze that is surrounding me – it has taken over me.
The entity is overriding all signals in my rig and forcing its presence onto me, making sure I know it's watching me by showing me images of myself. 
I need to consult the 100porcent MGK-TV research team to see if they have had such an event over the course of their research or if something is happening now. The overpowering signal is strangely familiar... They might know something about it. 

... i don't like this one bit...
